{"tid":2501373,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"武裝組織不滿華垂涎資源","createTime":"2021-04-23T10:18:38.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-23T10:49:54.000Z","uid":25558,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"8c3df80a54c8925cc8498241f35a75c1041b1167","tid":2501373,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T10:18:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210423/VDGFR3MHYNAEZDQRDBEOBS6DVM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210423%2FVDGFR3MHYNAEZDQRDBEOBS6DVM%2F&d=9fgUEJ%2BH4pM5xz2q5iffzhSC%2F35X4DTIU%2BW3we%2FDSDs%3D&h=37709c9a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210423%2FVDGFR3MHYNAEZDQRDBEOBS6DVM%2F&h=8751b5d8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210423/VDGFR3MHYNAEZDQRDBEOBS6DVM/</a><br />\n<br />\n武裝組織不滿華垂涎資源<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/7u9sQHXUH4Q-pwQ_wqhRRZ3qV1o=/510x287/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/4C2OYVR5V5B4PM5HNWL4D7VSTM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F7u9sQHXUH4Q-pwQ_wqhRRZ3qV1o%3D%2F510x287%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F4C2OYVR5V5B4PM5HNWL4D7VSTM.jpg&h=cac34164&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■爆炸後一名男子安撫死者家屬。<br />\n<br />\n【話你知】俾路支人是巴基斯坦四大種族之一，俾路支省雖是巴基斯坦最貧窮的省分之一，但天然氣、煤炭等資源豐富。該省與阿富汗、伊朗接壤，又有瓜達爾港連接阿拉伯海，帶來中國一帶一路的投資，同時省內有大量武裝組織謀求獨立，包括巴基斯坦塔利班及「俾路支解放軍」（BLA）。兩者均指摘中國投資未能惠及當地人，反而透過投資來掠奪資源，故過往有行動針對中國。<br />\n<br />\n巴基斯坦塔利班支持中國視為恐怖組織的「東突厥斯坦伊斯蘭運動（東突），多次發聲明批評中國的新疆人權問題，故有分析稱他們透過打擊中巴經濟走廊，增加其地區影響。至於BLA，他們曾襲擊瓜達爾港一間五星級酒店，造成至少五死，直認是針對中國投資者。中國三大交易所持股的巴基斯坦卡拉奇證券交易所去年6月亦遭BLA襲擊，四名持手榴彈及自動步槍的槍手闖入亂槍掃射，最少七人死亡。<br />\n<br />\nBBC/外交家雜誌"},{"pid":"6573f3979e06c6e4d7b9de800ef29e2c2d7eaab6","tid":2501373,"uid":282930,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T10:30:00.00